long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🎉🛍️ Download high-definition images or videos from product pages with a single click to zip file, export image or video infos to csv file. 📸🎥

Key Features:
1️⃣ Effortless HD Image Downloads: Download image one by one or download all high-definition images associated with a Target product to a zip file in one go. Easily curate your personal collection and find inspiration. 💫✨

2️⃣Convenient Video Downloads: Save captivating product videos for offline viewing or analysis. Download videos with a single click and enjoy them at your convenience. 🎥🔽

3️⃣ Export Image or Video URLs and Information: Gather comprehensive data about Target products. Export image URLs and associated information with one click. Create a CSV file for analysis, research, or any other purpose. 📊📋

Enhance your work experience with our feature-rich extension. Take control of your business journey today! 🚀💻
